即将旅行？这就是您应该购买 Apple AirTag 的原因https://www.billboard.com/shop/best-airtags-gps-tracking-devices-where-to-buy-1235199073/Latifah Muhammad Wed, 21 Feb 2024 02:30:00 +0000 CultureProduct Recommendationsairtagsappletravel https://www.billboard.com/?p=1235199073 This tiny gadget can make a big difference in how you travel.<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p class="pmc-ecomm-disclaimer">所有特色产品和服务均由编辑独立选择。然而，Billboard 可能会收到通过其零售链接下的订单的佣金，并且零售商可能会收到某些用于会计目的的可审计数据。</p><p class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "> <a rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow" href="https://amzn.to/3k8AvPH?asc_source=feed&amp;asc_campaign=feed&amp;asc_refurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.billboard.com%2Fshop%2Fbest-airtags-gps-tracking-devices-where-to-buy-1235199073%2F" target="_blank">Apple AirTags</a>在<a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.billboard.com/culture/product-recommendations/travel-necessities-to-buy-online-1235189409/" target="_blank">旅行必备品</a>清单中名列前茅。这款售价 29 美元的硬币形状的小工具可以让您轻松追踪您的行李和其他可能在运输过程中丢失的物品。</p><p class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   ">西南航空公司在 2022 年假期期间取消了 13,000 多个航班，导致乘客滞留（有时一次滞留数天）并与行李分离，之后 AirTags 开始被抢购一空。</p><p class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   ">这场旅行灾难演变成一场旅行噩梦，导致<a rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow" href="https://www.cnbc.com/2023/12/18/southwest-fined-140-million-for-last-years-holiday-meltdown.html" data-type="link" data-id="https://www.cnbc.com/2023/12/18/southwest-fined-140-million-for-last-years-holiday-meltdown.html" target="_blank">西南航空被处以 1.4 亿美元的罚款</a>，而苹果公司却意外获得了销售胜利。当时， <a rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow" href="https://trends.google.com/trends/explore?geo=US&amp;q=%2Fg%2F11ftgrlhp8#RELATED_QUERIES" target="_blank">Google</a>对<a rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow" href="https://www.businessinsider.com/southwest-flight-cancellations-lost-baggage-apple-air-tags-sales-amazon-2023-1" target="_blank">AirTags 的搜索量激增</a>，AirTags 在亚马逊<a rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow" href="https://amzn.to/3w2usza?asc_source=feed&amp;asc_campaign=feed&amp;asc_refurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.billboard.com%2Fshop%2Fbest-airtags-gps-tracking-devices-where-to-buy-1235199073%2F" target="_blank">最畅销电子产品</a>排行榜上占据了两个位置。</p><p class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   ">当航空公司丢失行李或称行李位于其他地点时，AirTags 可以帮助乘客<a rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow" href="https://thepointsguy.com/news/how-airtags-help-delayed-bags/" target="_blank">找到行李</a>。但它们不仅对旅行有用。</p><p class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "> AirTags 可帮助您对个人物品进行某种数字控制。这意味着您可以使用 AirTag 来查找或跟踪您的钱包、背包、钱包和其他较小的物品，甚至是汽车等较大的物品。 </p><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img decoding="async" width="1498" height="1500" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Apple-Airtag.jpg?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-1235199082" style="width:389px;height:389px" srcset="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Apple-Airtag.jpg 1498w, https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Apple-Airtag.jpg?resize=150,150 150w, https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Apple-Airtag.jpg?resize=300,300 300w" sizes="(min-width: 87.5rem) 1000px, (min-width: 78.75rem) 681px, (min-width: 48rem) 450px, (max-width: 48rem) 100vw"><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">亚马逊</figcaption></figure></div><div class="buy-now-v2 version-2 no_price"><a class=" buy-now-button-v2 version-2 no_price" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0933BVK6T?tag=billboard0ad-20&amp;linkCode=ogi&amp;th=1&amp;psc=1&amp;language=en_US&amp;asc_source=feed&amp;asc_campaign=feed&amp;asc_refurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.billboard.com%2Fshop%2Fbest-airtags-gps-tracking-devices-where-to-buy-1235199073%2F" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" custom-ga-data='{"1pd":true,"category":"article-page","details":"Apple AirTag","label":"buy-now","event_type_label":"Affiliate","url":true,"product":{"dimension1":"%=href=%","name":"Appl