>顶级音乐律师强力玩家选择奖将与<em>Billboard</em>年度顶级音乐律师行业最具影响力律师排名同时进行，该排名将于 3 月份公布。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <em>Billboard</em>于2023年推出了强力玩家选择奖，包括<a  rel="noreferrer noopener"  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/brandon-silverstein-2023-billboard-power-players-choice-award/"  target="_blank"  >玩家选择奖、</a> <a  rel="noreferrer noopener"  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/morgan-wallen-manager-seth-england-country-power-players-award/"  target="_blank"  >乡村强力玩家选择奖、</a> <a  rel="noreferrer noopener"  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/quality-control-pierre-thomas-rb-hip-hop-power-players-award/"  target="_blank"  >R&amp;B/嘻哈强力玩家选择奖</a>和<a  rel="noreferrer noopener"  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/maluma-manager-walter-kolm-latin-power-players-choice-award/"  target="_blank"  >拉丁强力玩家选择奖</a>。本月早些时候，由同行投票选出的环球音乐集团董事长兼首席执行官<strong>乔迪·格尔森 (Jody Gerson)</strong>荣获<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/umpg-jody-gerson-billboard-power-players-choice-award/"  >2024 年 Power Power 玩家选择奖</a>。今年，该奖项的范围扩大到还涵盖顶级音乐律师和国际实力人物。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <a  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/top-music-lawyers-power-players-choice-award-vote/"  target="_blank"  rel="noreferrer noopener"  ><span data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" class="TextRun Underlined SCXW120578187 BCX0" style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 14pt;line-height: 22.6625px;font-family: Calibri, Calibri_EmbeddedFont, Calibri_MSFontService, sans-serif"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW120578187 BCX0" data-ccp-charstyle="Hyperlink" style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px">立即投票</span></span></a><span data-contrast="auto" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" class="TextRun SCXW120578187 BCX0" style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 14pt;line-height: 22.6625px;font-family: Calibri, Calibri_EmbeddedFont, Calibri_MSFontService, sans-serif">，如果您还不是</span><span data-contrast="auto" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" class="TextRun SCXW120578187 BCX0" style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 14pt;font-style: italic;line-height: 22.6625px;font-family: Calibri, Calibri_EmbeddedFont, Calibri_MSFontService, sans-serif">Billboard Pro</span>的会员<span data-contrast="auto" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" class="TextRun SCXW120578187 BCX0" style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 14pt;line-height: 22.6625px;font-family: Calibri, Calibri_EmbeddedFont, Calibri_MSFontService, sans-serif">，</span> <a  class="Hyperlink SCXW120578187 BCX0"  rel="noreferrer noopener"  style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;color: inherit"  href="https://www.billboard.com/subscribe/"  target="_blank"  ><span data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" class="TextRun Underlined SCXW120578187 BCX0" style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-size: 14pt;line-height: 22.6625px;font-family: Calibri, Calibri_EmbeddedFont, Calibri_MSFontService, sans-serif"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW120578187 BCX0" data-ccp-charstyle="Hyperlink" style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px">请在此处加入</span></span></a><span data-contrast="auto" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" class="TextR