签名：乔恩·帕迪 (Jon Pardi) 加盟 WME、英国摇滚乐队 Sleep Token Bunk 与 RCA https://www.billboard.com/business/business-news/jon-pardi-signs-wme-sleep-token-rca-music-artist-deals-1235611187/Chris Eggertsen Wed, 21 Feb 2024 01:17:08 +0000 BusinessBusiness Newslabel signingsSignedsignings https://www.billboard.com/?p=1235611187 Other ink this week: Crowded House, Wyatt Ellis, Morgan Jay and more.<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> Capitol Records 纳什维尔艺术家<strong><a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/jon-pardi/"  >Jon Pardi</a></strong> （《Head Over Boots》、《Heartache on the Dance Floor》）与<strong>WME</strong>签约，并将由该机构的多个部门代表，包括巡演、品牌合作、电视、电影和数字部门。 Pardi 由 Red Light Management 的<strong>Gaines Sturdivant</strong>和 C3 Management 的<strong>Charlie Walker</strong>管理。 <em>——杰西卡·尼克尔森</em></p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>英国摇滚乐队<strong><a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/sleep-token/"  >Sleep Token</a></strong>与<strong>RCA 唱片公司</strong>签约。该团体是一个匿名的蒙面团体，由一位名叫 Vessel 的歌手领导。 Sleep Token 由 Future History Management 的经理<strong>Ryan Richards</strong>代表；北美和南美独立艺术家集团的预订代理<strong>Nick Storch</strong> ；以及 UTA 世界其他地区的订票代理<strong>Paul Ryan</strong> 。它之前已与 Spinefarm/Universal 签约。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img decoding="async" class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/themes/vip/pmc-billboard-2021/assets/public/lazyload-fallback.gif" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Darren-Kiely-cr-Matthew-Berinato-press-2024-billboard-pro-1260.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="达伦·凯利" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max">索尼音乐纳什维尔推出 Free Flight Records——一个新的非乡村唱片公司</h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lr