		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <strong>MNRK</strong>还与克利夫兰另类金属乐队<strong>A Killer&#39;s Confession</strong>签约，为其全球 MNRK Heavy 印记。该协议下的第一首单曲《Greed》将于 3 月 15 日发行，专辑定于秋季发行。乐队由 TKO 的预订代理<strong>安德鲁·古德弗兰德 (Andrew Goodfriend)</strong>代表。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img decoding="async" class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/themes/vip/pmc-billboard-2021/assets/public/lazyload-fallback.gif" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/kylie-minogue-press-credit-ed-cooke-2023-billboard-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="凯莉·米洛" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max">凯莉·米洛与 UTA 签约</h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 2024年2月20日</time></div></div></div><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>法国出生的歌手、模特、舞者和演员<strong>Lucky Love</strong>与<strong>UTA</strong>签约，在除法国之外的全球范围内进行现场表演。 Love 于 2023 年 4 月发行了他的首张 EP <em>《TENDRESSE》</em> ；他与贝伦音乐签约。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
