顶级音乐律师强力玩家选择奖：投票选出最具影响力的律师（半决赛入围者） https://www.billboard.com/pro/top-music-lawyers-power-players-choice-award-vote/Colin Stutz Wed, 21 Feb 2024 01:16:02 +0000 BusinessLegal Newsbillboard propower playersPower Players&#039; Choice AwardsTop Music Lawyers https://www.billboard.com/?post_type=billboard_pro_post&p=1235603456 The peer-voted award allows the music business to participate in Billboard's Top Music Lawyers ranking of the industry's most influential executives.<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> 《公告<em>牌</em>》同行投票选出的“顶级音乐律师强力玩家选择奖”半决赛投票现已开放，该奖项旨在表彰行业同行认为在过去一年中最具影响力的律师。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <em>Billboard Pro</em>会员（无论是现有会员还是新会员）每轮每人可获得一票。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img decoding="async" class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/themes/vip/pmc-billboard-2021/assets/public/lazyload-fallback.gif" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Billboard-Top-Ballers-featured-1240.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="顶级音乐律师强力玩家选择奖：投票选出最佳律师" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max">音乐和体育顶尖选手：高管、运动员和艺术家</h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 2024年2月20日</time></div></div></div><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>经过公开征集提名后，15 名半决赛入围者现在将参加顶级音乐律师强力玩家选择奖的第二轮投票。得票数前五名的选手将进入决赛。半决赛投票将于三月结束。 3 日晚上 11:59（美国东部时间）</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>顶级音乐律师强力玩家选择奖将与<em>Billboard</em>年度顶级音乐律师行业最具影响力律师排名同时进行，该排名将于 3 月份公布。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>在这里投票： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" frameborder="0" width="100%" height="600" scrolling="auto" allowtransparency="true" src="https://billboardpd.survey.fm/top-music-lawyers-power-players-choice-award-2023-semifinals-15?iframe=1"> <a  href="https://billboardpd.survey.fm/top-music-lawyers-power-players-choice-award-2023-semifinals-15"  rel="nofollow"  target="_blank"  >查看调查</a></iframe></p><p
