		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>第三轮也是最后一轮投票将于三月开始。 4. 投票于美国东部时间 3 月 17 日晚上 11:59 结束。</p></div> ;
为什么爱莉安娜·格兰德和玛丽亚·凯莉的《是的，然后？》混音是天后二人组的一个完整循环时刻https://www.billboard.com/media/podcasts/ariana-grande-mariah-carey-yes-and-remix-pop-shop-podcast-1235611181/Katie Atkinson Wed, 21 Feb 2024 00:34:40 +0000 MediaPodcastsMusic NewspodcastsPoppop shopPop Shop Podcast - New Every Tuesday https://www.billboard.com/?p=1235611181 On the new Billboard Pop Shop Podcast, Katie &#38; Keith are talking about the buzzy team-up, as well as Dua Lipa's new "Training Season" single &#38; video.<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
><a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/ariana-grande/"  >爱莉安娜·格兰德 (Ariana Grande)</a>凭借梦幻般的流行歌曲和高亢的口哨音调，自 2013 年首次亮相以来，人们将她与<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/mariah-carey/"  >玛丽亚·凯莉 (Mariah Carey)</a>进行比较。当然，在此后的十多年里，格兰德为自己赢得了巨大的声誉 - 所以两位排行榜冠军歌手在刚刚发布的<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/music/pop/ariana-grande-mariah-carey-yes-and-remix-stream-it-now-1235609305/"  >Grande 的“Yes, And?”混音版</a>中联手，这有点像一个完整的循环时刻。 <a  href="https://www.billboard.com/music/pop/ariana-grande-mariah-carey-yes-and-remix-stream-it-now-1235609305/"  >单身的</a>。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>在新的 Billboard Pop Shop 播客中，Katie 和 Keith 谈论了为什么混音如此有意义，从两位艺术家长期以来对彼此的钦佩，到参考 90 年代早期的歌曲制作对 Carey 的 90 年代早期有意义起源。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img decoding="async" class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/themes/vip/pmc-billboard-2021/assets/public/lazyload-fallback.gif" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mariah-Carey-and-Ariana-Grande-cr-Katia-Temkin-press-2024-billboard-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="玛丽亚·凯莉和爱莉安娜·格兰德" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max">粉丝们选择爱莉安娜·格兰德和玛丽亚·凯莉的《是的，然后？》混音成为本周的最爱…… </h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 2024年2月20日</time></div></div></div><p
